title: Rosemary & Olive Oil Chicken Tenders
directions: flour in shallow dish. Whisk eggs and water in second shallow dish until blended; combine cracker crumbs and parsley in third dish.

foil-covered baking sheet with cooking spray. Dip 1 chicken tender in flour, turning to evenly coat chicken; shake gently to remove excess flour. Add chicken to egg mixture, then crumb mixture, turning to evenly coat chicken with each ingredient. Place on prepared baking sheet. Repeat with remaining chicken tenders.
25 min. or until chicken is done. Serve with mayonnaise.
ingredients: 24 TRISCUIT Rosemary & Olive Oil Crackers, finely crushed
